1. Lovac *puca* u divlju svinju. (The hunter *shoots* at the wild boar.)
2. Vlasnik imanja zaposlio je lovca *da bi* kontrolisao brojnost divljači. (The owner of the estate hired a hunter *to control* the number of game animals.)
3. Lovac je *ulovio* jelena. (The hunter *caught* a deer.)
4. Moja braća su *lovci* i vole da love srne. (My brothers are *hunters* and they love to hunt deer.)
5. Prijatelj mi je *poklonio* lovački nož. (My friend *gave me* a hunting knife as a gift.)
6. Lovac je *pretrčao* šumu u potrazi za divljači. (The hunter *ran through* the forest in search of game animals.)
7. Voleo bih da imam *lovnu pušku* kao što ima moj otac. (I would like to have a *hunting rifle* like my father does.)
8. Lovac je *streljao* fazana. (The hunter *shot* a pheasant.)
9. Najveći trofej koji je lovčev otac ikad ulovio bio je medved. (The biggest trophy that the hunter's father ever *caught* was a bear.)
10. Lovac je *namamio* divlje svinje sa hranom. (The hunter *lured* the wild boars with food.)